{
  "stem": "21978.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And if I was told to do something, and I didn't know to, and I was told off, and then the matron was called to sort it out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I was called Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Kunewalder, because the matron was very-- you know, she didn't call us by first name.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Kunewalder.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And we tried to-- to-- to live like young people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Annetta, my sister, actually married a survivor who we met in Auschwitz when we were the twins, and on the twins barracks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "One twin died, and there was sent a couple of men with a stretcher from other camp to bring this corpse to the postmortem, or I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And when these men came, we found out that we could talk to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We found out they are Czech.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And we spoke the Czech, a couple of pleasantries.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And when they went away, we found out that they were from-- from where they come or whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was the last time-- first and last time, we saw them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after the war when we had our diplomas, and we went to celebrate, to dance, a gentleman came to my sister and said, would you dance with me?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, I don't recollect.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, lift your sleeve.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If your number is similar to mine, we were together at the same time at the same-- and he recognized her.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a romance after that, and she married him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were-- that was her husband who came with her to Australia and fathered her children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we met there, in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was shorter than it should have been.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It should have been for three years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after the war, they made everything shorter to have nurses.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
